Bridget.SiebertTHE SA Legion of Military Veterans extends its thanks to the public of Pietermaritzburg for their generous support of the Delville Wood collection that was held on 16 July, which raised R5 000. Thank you to all who helped with the collections, for giving up their time, and to the centres and businesses that allowed us to collect at their premises.Ex-servicemen and their families, who are genuinely in need, shall benefit from your kind generosity.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.